|title=The Blood Circulation of Animals Possessing Chlorocruorin
|journal=[[Proceedings_of_the_Royal_Society_B|Proceedings of the Royal Society B]]|volume=112|issue=779
|pages=479–495|date=1933-04-01
|pmid=|doi=10.1098/rspb.1938.0042
|jstor=81599}}</ref><ref name=RFEwer>{{Cite journal
|author=R. F. Ewer, H. Munro Fox
|title=On the Function of Chlorocruorin
|journal=[[Proceedings_of_the_Royal_Society_B|Proceedings of the Royal Society B]]
|volume=129
|issue=855
|pages=137–153
|date=1940-08-09
|pmid=
|doi=10.1098/rspb.1940.0033
|jstor=82389}}</ref><ref name=DWEwer>{{cite journal
|author=D.W. Ewer
|title=The blood systems of Sabella and Spirographis
|journal=Quarterly Journal of Microscopical Science
|volume=82
