血綠素是一個巨大分子，但不存在於紅血球內，而是自由地在血漿內漂浮<ref name="pmid11294828" /><ref name=Lamy>{{Cite journal
|author=Lamy JN, Green BN, Toulmond A, Wall JS, Weber RE, Vinogradov SN
|title=Giant Hexagonal Bilayer Hemoglobins
|journal=Chem Rev
|volume=96
|issue=8
|pages=3113–3124
|date=1996-12-19
|pmid=11848854 |doi=10.1021/cr9600058 |language=en }}</ref>。其結構跟{{le|無脊椎動物血紅蛋白|erythrocruorin}}非常相像；而無脊椎動物血紅蛋白的結構又跟[[肌紅蛋白|肌紅蛋白]]（myoglobin）只有幾個subunits的差異。它本身由多組16-17[[kDa|kDa]]的類肌紅蛋白單元排列，形成一個有超過一百個單元的巨型複雜構造，蛋白間有互連，總重量超過3600[[kDa|kDa]]。The only significant difference between chlorocruorin and erythrocruorin is that chlorocruorin carries an abnormal heme group structure<ref name="pmid11294828">{{Cite journal |author=Pallavicini A, Negrisolo E, Barbato R |title=The primary structure of globin and linker chains from the chlorocruorin of the polychaete Sabella spallanzanii |journal=J. Biol. Chem. |volume=276 |issue=28 |pages=26384–90 |date=July 2001 |pmid=11294828 |doi=10.1074/jbc.M006939200 |url=http://www.jbc.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=11294828 |display-authors=etal |access-date=2016-03-17 |archive-date=2020-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200528051023/https://www.jbc.org/content/276/28/26384.long |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

